<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>UEL(Thailand) Co., Ltd. cooperated with the Thai-Nichi Institute of Technology in the event &quot;TNI Job Fair 2020&quot; for introducing about CADmeister&rsquo;s user companies in Thailand. There are various UEL (Thailand) &rsquo;s company partners who came to present their companies and available job positions, it was a great opportunity for the TNI newly graduated students who are looking for a suitable career.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>The companies that collaborated with us&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1. <u>AWS Machinary&amp; Santech Asia</u></strong></p><p><strong>2. <u>TamatsuuraPattern (Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><strong>3. <u>Horiuchi Technology(Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><strong>4. <u>Toyoda Seiko (Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><strong>5. <u>Nagano Precision (Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Thank all of our partners and the Thai-Nichi Institute of Technology students that were interested in joining our event this time.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>